headline: CHIPOTLE TO PREMIERE ALEX WARREN'S NEW ALBUM YOU'LL BE ALRIGHT, KID AT RESTAURANTS WORLDWIDE ON JULY 17
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) today announced it is teaming up with singer-songwriter and brand superfan Alex Warren to host a first-of-its-kind listening party for his new album, You'll Be Alright, Kid, this Thursday, July 17. In one of the biggest and most unique listening parties in music history, Warren will become the first artist to premiere a new album at nearly 4,000 Chipotle locations across the U.S., Canada, UK and France. See Warren's announcement post here.
